data.description: Great opportunity to own this incredible single level home now on the market in popular Avondale! Highly upgraded waiting just for you. Providing great curb appeal and easy care gravel front landscaping. Set foot inside to find an open concept interior complete with 4 bed, 2 bath, vaulted ceilings, living/dining area, designer paint tones, and so much natural light. Well maintained eat-in kitchen has everything you need; white matching appliances, honey oak cabinetry, plenty counter space, breakfast bar, recessed lighting, and centered island. Bright master bedroom includes a spotless full bathroom with walk-in closet. Peaceful backyard with covered patio is ready for you to make it your own. This home is the one you have been waiting for. Hurry start calling to schedule your showing now!
